  <?dbhtml filename="crunchbang-wallpapers.html"?>

  <title>crunchbang-wallpapers-&crunchbang-wallpapers-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This package provides a selection of wallpapers and images from CrunchBang
      Linux for use as backgrounds.
    </para>

