  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install crunchbang-wallpapers by running the following commands, as the
      <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>tar xvf backgrounds.tar.gz -C /usr/share --no-same-owner</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

